<h2>Help</h2>
<p><strong>How to Browse and Search:</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Explore Categories:</strong>
        <p>On the homepage, you can browse our available content by category. Just click on any category to see more.</p>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Use the Search Bar:</strong>
        <p>If you’re looking for something specific, type your query in the search bar at the top of the page. Hit "Enter" or click the search icon to see results.</p>
    </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>How to Make a Purchase (If Applicable):</strong></p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Select an Item:</strong>
        <p>Browse through our products or services, and click on the item you wish to purchase.</p>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Add to Cart:</strong>
        <p>Once you’re on the product page, select the quantity and click "Add to Cart."</p>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Proceed to Checkout:</strong>
        <p>When you’re ready to buy, click on the shopping cart icon at the top of the page and click "Proceed to Checkout."</p>
    </li>
    <li><strong>Complete Your Purchase:</strong>
        <p>Enter your shipping information and payment details to finalize your order.</p>
    </li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Contact:</strong></p>
<ul>

        <p>If you encounter any issues or have questions, please refer to the FAQ section or contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@petstore.com">support@petstore.com</a>.</p>
    

</ul>